== Introduction ==
LandmarkShops is an E-commerce website based out of [[Dubai]], [[UAE]]. The site was launched as the online retail arm of the [[Landmark Group]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://gulfnews.com/business/retail/landmark-nails-down-an-online-presence-1.1338577|title=Landmark nails down an online presence}}</ref>

== History ==
LandmarkShops was launched in December 2012 as the Group<U+2019>s venture into online retail.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://gulfnews.com/business/retail/landmark-nails-down-an-online-presence-1.1338577|title=Landmark nails down an online presence}}</ref>

== Business, Brands and Features ==
LandmarkShops allows customer to shop for products from [[Babyshop]], Splash and Emax.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/biz/inside.asp?xfile=/data/uaebusiness/2013/July/uaebusiness_July65.xml&section=uaebusiness|title=Landmark Group unveils new e-commerce portal}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.godubai.com/citylife/press_release_page.asp?pr=78053|title=LandmarkShops Takes UAE's Top Brands Online}}</ref> The site incorporates Shukran, the Landmark Group<U+2019>s loyalty programme.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://snd.landmarkgroup.com/earn-shukran-points-on-all-of-your-landmarkshops-com-orders/|title=Earn Shukran points on all of your LandmarkShops.com orders}}</ref>

== Categories ==
As of September 2014, LandmarkShops offers over 30,000 products for sale across women and men<U+2019>s fashion, baby and child, toys and books, electronics, appliances and personal care categories.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/biz/inside.asp?xfile=/data/uaebusiness/2013/July/uaebusiness_July65.xml&section=uaebusiness|title=Landmark Group unveils new e-commerce portal}}</ref>

== Locations ==
LandmarkShops is headquartered in Dubai and has logistics and operations across the UAE.

